      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $\\alpha,\\beta,\\gamma \\in \\R$ tels que $\\alpha+\\beta+\\gamma = \\pi$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha,\\beta,\\gamma \\in \\R\\)</span> tels que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha+\\beta+\\gamma = \\pi\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e6d2a85d-ceed-4871-9f9c-7258dad007b8",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Démontrer que : $1 - \\cos\\alpha + \\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma =\n                 4\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac\\beta2 \\cos\\frac\\gamma2$.",
        "html": "<p>Démontrer que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 - \\cos\\alpha + \\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma =\n                 4\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac\\beta2 \\cos\\frac\\gamma2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b3456d31-aff1-433f-adb8-7367db90ae63",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$1 - \\cos\\alpha = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta+\\gamma}2$,\n\n$\\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta-\\gamma}2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 - \\cos\\alpha = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta+\\gamma}2\\)</span>,</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\cos\\beta + \\cos\\gamma = 2\\sin\\frac\\alpha2 \\cos\\frac {\\beta-\\gamma}2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5e0453c8-ab1e-44c2-bcd7-e2d9ea651c79",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Simplifier $\\tan\\frac\\alpha2 \\tan\\frac\\beta2  +\n             \\tan\\frac\\beta2  \\tan\\frac\\gamma2 +\n             \\tan\\frac\\gamma2 \\tan\\frac\\alpha2 $.",
        "html": "<p>Simplifier <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\tan\\frac\\alpha2 \\tan\\frac\\beta2  +\n             \\tan\\frac\\beta2  \\tan\\frac\\gamma2 +\n             \\tan\\frac\\gamma2 \\tan\\frac\\alpha2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "94c03c31-c88e-4553-932f-1444cd44dbcd",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$=1$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(=1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
